    "title": "Hofu ya Bwana",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "hofu ya bwana",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Wakati Mose anatoa maagizo yake ya mwisho kwa watu wa Israeli kabla ya kifo chake, anawahimiza mara kwa mara &quot;kumcha BWANA&quot; (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:1-Deut6:13\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 6:1–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:21\">10:12–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:9-Deut31:13\">31:9–13</a>). Yoshua pia anatoa ushauri huo karibu na mwisho wa maisha yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14\">Yoshua 24:14</a>). <em>Hofu</em> inamaanisha heshima, hisia ya kushangazwa na kitu kikubwa, na wakati mwingine kuwa na hofu kubwa. Kumcha Bwana kunahusisha kuwa na ufahamu wa mamlaka na nguvu zake kila wakati. Kwa Waisraeli, kumcha Bwana kulimaanisha kutambua kwamba mafanikio yao yalitegemea kabisa Mungu.</p><p>Mada kuu ya Mithali inafupishwa katika maneno: “Kumcha BWANA ni mwanzo wa maarifa” (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">Mithali 1:7</a>). Hofu hii inawafanya watu wawe wanyenyekevu na wasio na kiburi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:7\">3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">15:33</a>). Kwa mtazamo huu, watu watamtii Mungu zaidi kuliko kutegemea maamuzi yao wenyewe. Kumcha Bwana kunatambua nafasi kuu ya Mungu katika mpangilio wa dunia. Mungu ni Muumba na Bwana wa kila kitu.</p><p>Hii ndiyo sababu <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1\">Zaburi 14:1</a> inawaita wale wanaomkataa Mungu “wapumbavu.” Wale wanaomcha Bwana wanapata hekima kwa sababu wanaelewa kuwa kila kitu kiko chini ya utawala wa Mungu na kinamtumikia. Hii si mtazamo tu, bali ni njia ya kuishi inayoheshimu nguvu na mamlaka ya Mungu na jukumu letu la mwisho kwake.</p><p>Hekima inahusishwa na uhusiano mzuri na Mungu. Vyote vinahitaji uchaguzi unaolingana na tabia ya Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:28\">Ayubu 28:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:2\">Mithali 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">Mhubiri 12:13</a>). Unataka hekima? Basi lazima uwe na uhusiano na yule ambaye ana hekima yote (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1-1Cor2:16\">1 Wakorintho 1:1–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:3\">Wakolosai 2:3</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:28\">Ayubu 28:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1\">Zaburi 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">111:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">Mithali 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:7\">3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:27\">10:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:2\">14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:26-Prov14:27\">26–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:16\">15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:33\">33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:23\">19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:4\">22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">Mhubiri 12:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1-Isa11:2\">Isaya 11:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:6\">33:6</a></p>",
